#ALIAS {miru} {mir}
#ALIAS {pouch} {use powder}
#ALIAS {rock} {gb rock; throw rock %1}
#ALIAS {candle} {gb candle; wield candle; use candle; wm}
#ALIAS {cand} {candle}
#ALIAS {candel} {candle}
